{"tid":2276041,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"解放軍駐港部隊進行野外訓練　裝甲車駛經市區","createTime":"2020-11-07T15:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T16:44:13.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"957ea3cee88593976aff7a2aede3d6b74b347f44","tid":2276041,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:17:28.000Z","msg":"內地傳媒報道，解放軍駐港部隊近期在本港的綜合訓練場，進行野外訓練，有效訓練部隊在實戰化條件下的作戰能力，提高裝甲分隊的整體戰術水平。<br />\n<br />\n從片段看到，多輛裝甲車駛出軍營，經過市區路面，在野外進行實彈射擊。<br />\n<br />\n報道形容今次的野外訓練戰味十足，按照抓好技術合練、務實戰術基礎、突出實彈射擊、提高行動能力的思路，鍛造過硬鐵甲精兵。<br />\n<br />\n報道又表示，今次演練不管是導彈、火炮、步槍、手槍，還是煙霧彈，都從難從嚴，從實戰出發，錘煉官兵快速反應能力，力爭做到百發百中，切實提升部隊履行香港防務的能力，演練極大考驗射手的觀察、判斷和快速反應能力，進一步提升裝甲分隊整體作戰水準。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558862-20201107.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558862-20201107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft28sFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=e0d7b0b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558862-20201107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ca88f724\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558862-20201107.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"8352b4a838a1b6c66ebbb25ab3b24b0611b13802","tid":2276041,"uid":76804,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:17:54.000Z","msg":"係野外摺被姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc983de686e33cae60c61039560008c2bf8121d","tid":2276041,"uid":79117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:18:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3fe034dacf245428283b88ea75396fff78e9c6fc","tid":2276041,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:19:05.000Z","msg":"3000次模擬戰"},{"pid":"f064a73cc470483f5c8ed8d8a9781ae438a6c17b","tid":2276041,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"repl